node.text: This interview, hosted by @coachdhillon (give him a follow!), covers how I built the @investearnsave page into a profitable business in just 1 year, as well as my thoughts on themes such as investing, education and self-development. It was a pleasure to be on his podcast and we decided to share it here to give it extra visibility.

node.text:
I love Mondays! Why?...⁣
⁣
All days are as enjoyable as each other for me, however, I relish Mondays.⁣
⁣
This is because the fact I can enjoy Mondays is testament to what I have built, and a reminder to keep working on the life I've built.⁣
⁣
I want everybody to enjoy Mondays.⁣
⁣
Do you enjoy Mondays?⁣
⁣
If you run an online business or a do a job you love, then yes you probably do!⁣
⁣
For most people this isn't the case.⁣
⁣
It can be.⁣
⁣
You can build up skills in your free time, either relevant to starting a business or relevant to a career you know you'd love.⁣
⁣
Then, once the skills are built up, you can grow a business or switch careers.⁣
⁣
It sounds overly simple, but if you genuinely attempt it for 2 years, I can almost guarantee good things will happen.⁣
⁣
Try it, and soon you too will love Mondays.⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Don’t miss a post 👉 @investearnsave⁣⁣⁣

node.text:
And how is he so rich? Two reasons:⁣
⁣
• Compounding.⁣
• Ownership.⁣
⁣
Allow me to break it down.⁣
⁣
Compounding - Compound interest is the mathematical formula that creates wealth. Most of you already know it but it helps to highlight just how important it is. It's the difference between living pay check to pay check for your whole life, and retiring young and wealthy.⁣
⁣
Ownership - This one requires a little more discussion. What people often fail to mention about Buffett's success is his role as a CEO and advisor to corporations. He's not your average investor putting in a bit of money here and there. His stake in companies often makes him the outright owner or at least, someone the company's board will listen to.⁣
⁣
Whilst, you can't buy large companies, you can have ownership over your own businesses, side hustles, social media pages, etc, to produce income on your own terms. This is probably more important than investing in stocks.⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Don’t miss a post 👉 @investearnsave⁣⁣⁣
⁣

node.text:
I'm not here to debate economics or Bezos' moral character, but to teach financial lessons so that you may better yourself, so here goes...⁣
⁣
Catastrophes are, well, catastrophic. ⁣
⁣
They can depress whole nations, even the whole world.⁣
⁣
And we saw this happen in 2020.⁣
⁣
But, for entrepreneurs. There is opportunity too.⁣
⁣
Some of the world's biggest companies were created during recessions. Like IBM and Microsoft.⁣
⁣
During 2020 we saw the success of companies like Amazon, Zoom, etc etc.⁣
⁣
You have to rise above the public mood, and see where the opportunity lies.⁣
⁣
Everyone inside?⁣
⁣
How can you make people's lives that little bit easier and more enjoyable whilst they're stuck inside.⁣
⁣
Answer that, you've got money.⁣
⁣
Economy is crashing and property prices have halved?⁣
⁣
This is a good time to buy, so when prices go back to their previous highs, you've doubled your money.⁣
⁣
You can't let yourself fall into the public mood during these moments, rise above it and thrive.⁣
⁣⁣
Don’t miss a post 👉 @investearnsave⁣⁣

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Investing | Finance | Business on September 12, 2021 tagging @investearnsave. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'SAVING: $10,000 SPENDING: $100 ME: "I'M BROKE" ONLY SOME WILL UNDERSTAND INVESTEARNSAVE'.

node.text:
To quote money Twitter "Few will understand"...⁣
⁣
I think most of you will understand, you follow money pages on Instagram, you see messages like this a lot.⁣
⁣
But does it mean you can't have fun?⁣
⁣
Does it mean you're the "richest person in the graveyard" but the poorest person in day to day life?⁣
⁣
No!⁣
⁣
When you focus on increasing your wealth, rather than just saving, suddenly your expendable income is still significant even when you invest the majority of your money.⁣
⁣
This can be best achieved by investing into things like your own business, side hustles, real estate, etc.⁣
⁣
And then for added security and passivity, invest a portion into the stock market.⁣
⁣
But if you focus on building wealth, rather than only saving to invest, you can live an enjoyable life whilst being someone invests most of their money.⁣
⁣
It might sound far fetched now but you'll get there!⁣
⁣⁣
Don’t miss a post 👉 @investearnsave⁣⁣

node.text:
I can't make it any simpler than this, you must fail if you want to succeed.⁣
⁣
By avoiding the risk of failure, by taking the easiest path through life, you're guaranteeing an unfilled existence. ⁣
⁣
You have to take leaps of faith, push towards your goals, take risks, and fail if you wish to succeed.⁣
⁣
Each failure makes you wiser, it allows you to fine-tune your gameplan and it prepares you to overcome future obstacles.⁣
⁣
If you want to succeed, increase your rate of failure.⁣
⁣
This isn't just random advice you hear but never gets practised. You can search for countless examples of successful people who failed many times before they had their success.⁣
⁣
On a personal level, I've been tinkering with ways of making money online since I was a little kid, most failed or had very low results.⁣
⁣
But I learned so much from them that eventually I was able to build a successful online business.⁣
⁣
And it's crazy how many of the skills I learned whilst failing other ways of making money, helped me with my successful business.⁣
⁣
Fail more.⁣
⁣⁣
Don’t miss a post 👉 @investearnsave⁣⁣

node.text:
You may not like Gates, but this quote is spot on...⁣
⁣
You're the only person with your exact goals.⁣
⁣
With your exact skills.⁣
⁣
With your exact experiences.⁣
⁣
And you're the only person at the same step in the journey of life.⁣
⁣
So, why compare yourself to others?⁣
⁣
It's either disheartening if they're so far above you.⁣
⁣
Or it allows for complacency if you're ahead of them.⁣
⁣
If you compete with yourself, you have to get better everyday.⁣
⁣
You're always motivated.⁣
⁣
It's tailored to you.⁣
⁣
You can win with each new step on your journey.⁣
⁣
Compete with yourself.⁣
⁣⁣
Don’t miss a post 👉 @investearnsave⁣⁣
